attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a shelf. They start by inspecting it, then mounting the straight black tubes onto the base of the shelf. They screw the first straight segments to the low part of the shelf, then the second straight segments to the lower part of the shelf. The student mounts the bottom plate at the base of the shelf and places the protection on the shelf before screwing the screws in. The student mounts the middle plate on the shelf and the upper shelf plate. The student rotates the parts
